'''Orli Shoshan''' (born [[July 23]], [[1974]]) is an actress who played [[Shaak Ti]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']] and in two non-[[canon]] deleted scenes in [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Revenge of the Sith'']].

In 2006, Orli joined [[Jeremy Bulloch]], [[Michael Sheard]], and [[David Prowse]] in the final part of UK fan film ''Order of the Sith: Downfall''. Orli played the part of a game-show host in a bar on [[Tatooine]]. The film was made in aid of Save the Children. She also appeared in the [[2009]] ''Star Wars'' reunion, hosted by [[Warwick Davis]].

